title: The One Where Lala Has An Epic Halloween Costume Fail
description:
Lala went to a Halloween party that turned out NOT to be just for adults (whoops), and shares her resulting epic costume fail! She shares some details from the opening titles shoot for the upcoming Vanderpump Rules season, weighs in on the RHOBH reunion & Lisa Rinna hate, schools an old troll who dared to drop in on her DMs, and dreams about expanding her family!
